altername_name: DJ Max Portable Emotional Sense: Clazziquai Edition
name: DJ Max Portable Clazziquai Edition
overview: DJMax Portable Clazziquai Edition is a music video game published and developed by Pentavision in South Korea for the PlayStation Portable released on October 20, 2008. This is the third title for the PlayStation Portable from in the DJMax Portable series after DJMax Portable 2. The game features songs from the Korean band Clazziquai.
